'''EA Salt Lake'''，是美国犹他州盐湖城的一个游戏开发商。该工作室为[[艺电|艺电]]所有。

1992年，EA Salt Lake由该工作室的总裁Vance Cook创立，<ref name="studiomoby">[http://www.mobygames.com/company/headgate-studios-inc Headgate Studios profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mobygames.com/company/headgate-studios-inc |date=20061214111447 }} at [[MobyGames|MobyGames]]</ref>当时名为Headgate Studios。Vance Cook曾是Access Software旗下高尔夫模拟游戏的程序员，因此他有足够的知识和经验知道如何制作高尔夫游戏。<ref>{{moby developer|id=1288|name=Vance Cook}}</ref>Headgate的第一个产品是PentaCalc，该软件是[[Windows系统|Windows系统]]的科学计算器。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://headgatestudios.com/projects.html |title=Headgate's website list of projects |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2011-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720142821/http://www.headgatestudios.com/projects.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

1996年到1999年，Headgate开发高尔夫游戏并在Sierra Entertainment的Sierra's Front Page Sports brand中发行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pc/sports/frontpagesportsgolf/index.html |title=Front Page Golf review @ gamespot.com |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929161050/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/sports/frontpagesportsgolf/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1996年4月该工作室被Sierra Entertainment收购。高尔夫游戏后来被冠名为PGA锦标赛高尔夫球场。在1999年2月22日Sierra Entertainment宣布公司进行重组，出售该工作室出售给Vance Cook，于是该工作室成为新的独立公司。<ref name="Headgate company history">{{Cite web |url=http://headgatestudios.com/company.html |title=Headgate company history |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2007-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070813045456/http://www.headgatestudios.com/company.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2000年，该工作室开始通过[[艺电|艺电]]出版游戏。该工作室在PC的高尔夫游戏引擎的基础上开发Tiger Woods PGA Tour。该游戏的2007年版本由EA分配去开发PC，PS2，Wii和Xbox版本，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/tiger-woods-pga-tour-07 |title=Gamespot details of Tiger Woods PGA Tour 07 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920073037/http://www.mobygames.com/game/tiger-woods-pga-tour-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和PC，PS2和Wii为2008年版本则被EA分配去开发PC，PS2，Wii（Xbox版本则被腰斩）<ref name="Headgate company history" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/tiger-woods-pga-tour-08 |title=Gamespot details of Tiger Woods PGA Tour 08 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922212006/http://www.mobygames.com/game/tiger-woods-pga-tour-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

从2001年至2007年，该工作室负责开发EA Sports Tiger Woods golf的每一个Windows版本，并获得业界评论家的好评，获得了众多的行业奖项。<ref>[http://www.gamespot.com/pc/sports/pgachampionshipgolf2000/index.html?q=PGA%20Championship%20Golf%202000 ''PGA Championship Golf 2000'' review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamespot.com/pc/sports/pgachampionshipgolf2000/index.html?q=PGA%20Championship%20Golf%202000 |date=20110524192717 }} from [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]</ref><ref>[http://www.sgn.cc/golf/tiger_woods_2001/review.shtml ''Tiger Woods 2001 PGA Tour'' review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sgn.cc/golf/tiger_woods_2001/review.shtml |date=20160303204620 }} from Sports Gaming Network</ref><ref>[http://pc.ign.com/articles/354/354044p1.html ''Tiger Woods 2002'' Review] {{Wayback|url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/354/354044p1.html |date=20120406173231 }} from [[IGN|IGN]]</ref><ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=111367 ''Tiger Woods PGA Tour 2003'' review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=111367 |date=20071030095954 }} from [[GameSpy|GameSpy]]</ref><ref>[http://pc.ign.com/articles/451/451107p1.html ''Tiger Woods PGA Tour 2004''] {{Wayback|url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/451/451107p1.html |date=20120822155910 }} from IGN</ref><ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=438951 ''Tiger Woods PGA TOUR 2005'' review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=438951 |date=20071107121604 }} from [[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]</ref><ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=428275 ''Tiger Woods PGA Tour 2005''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=428275 |date=20071013164624 }} from Game Rankings</ref>

2006年12月1日，该工作室被艺电收购。该工作室被改名为EA Salt Lake。该工作室的开发工作焦点为[[任天堂|任天堂]]的新主机Wii。<ref>[http://www.gamespot.com/news/6162544.html "EA forms Wii-centric studio"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/6162544.html |date=20061206040339 }} from [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]</ref>

2010年7月21日，该工作室从犹他州Bountiful搬到犹他州盐湖城。<ref>[http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/money/49968208-79/electronic-lake-salt-game.html.csp "Electronic Arts opens Salt Lake City office"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/money/49968208-79/electronic-lake-salt-game.html.csp |date=20160304025012 }} from [[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]]</ref>

